alth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy Allah, that Allah guides a man through you is better for you than a herd of expensive red camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3009, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2406 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/10\/akhirah-those-he-loved\/","url_meta":{"origin":5952,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Love: One is with loved ones in the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A bedouin\u00a0asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhen is the Hour?\u201d The Prophet\u00a0said, \u201cWhat have you prepared for it?\u201d The man said, \u201cLove for Allah and his messenger.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou will be with those whom you love.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3006,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/22\/jihad-in-way-of-allah-better-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":5952,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Striving for Allah is better than the world","author":"Abu Amina Eli